  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428840/extras/2551fa7c0d130fd64aa83c938686fd98.webp?t=1616084413\" width=180 height=50 /></span><br><br><strong>10mg</strong> is a collection of 10 minute long games.<br><br><strong>SNAAAK</strong> is a short atmospheric Snakevania.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428840/extras/e6d5f3e62954bca85cbdab83e04ba9bb.webp?t=1616084413\" width=400 height=60 /></span><br><br>Traverse a forgotten laboratory while encarnating a formless critter.<br>Experience a study on snake’s mechanics that explores different takes and turns on the core of its design as you roam through an extensive metroidvania setting.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Smooth Gameplay<br></li><li>An ethereal underground lab filled with mysterious hazards<br></li><li>Evocative ambience and sound design<br></li><li>Non-linear exploration<br></li><li>Full Controller Support</li></ul>",
